      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll dig into executeTrade. i'm also worried about the raw pointers in general, feels risky for this kind of high-speed stuff. how would i refactor this using std::unique_ptr so i don't have to manually manage the delete everywhere? can you show me a quick example of how the new function would look?",
